Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take aim and fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NStraw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES gasping, murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] That won't work on me!\NI told ya I was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--? You wanna tell me\Njust who the hell you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Morgan versus Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the Mysterious\NPretty Girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] You're gonna be\NKing of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be completely\Noutta you rubbery mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have any idea\Nwhat that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,King of the Pirates means\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it mean\Nanything other than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NHuh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when he first\Ntold me, it was shocking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's completely serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how he is, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause he actually seems\Nto have every intention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of becoming King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and obtaining the world's\Nultimate treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHere's what I promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell which was yours,\Nso I just took all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I use Santoryu, the\NThree-Swords Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take 'em already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just know that if\Nyou fight with me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be a\Ngovernment-defying villian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's either that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...or you're left out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and killed by the\Nmarines execution-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, the\Nson of the devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. 'Cause if\NI don't choose your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just end up\Ndead on these sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're finally\Ngonna join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY laughs]\N--Would you quit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right!\N--celebrating already
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and get these ropes off me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullets just bounced\Nright off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat's no ordinary\Nhuman like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have eaten one\Nof those Devil Fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've heard all\Nthose rumors about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The hidden treasure of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NThe Devil Fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who eat them are said
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to gain extraordinary,\Notherworldly abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NThe power to breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The power to cause tsunamis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors persist that there are\Nmany types of these fruits,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but next to nothing\Nis known about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that\Nthe secrets to them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,lie somewhere in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no\Nquestion about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hat has just\Nshowed us his Devil Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NCome on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They... got... these...\Nthings... on here tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Quit screwin' around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what\Nabilities they have,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all who oppose me are executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If the guns won't work, we chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The knots got tighter,\Ninstead of looser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme one of my\Ndamn swords, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]\NLuffy look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MARINES yelling]\N--[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[swords clang]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY gasps]\N--Wow! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Make one move and you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Today I officially\Nbecome a criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,having fought the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I can promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want you to know one\Nthing, while I'm with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing I dedicate myself\Nto is fulfilling my ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhich is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To be nothing less than the\Nworld's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If somewhere along the way\NI have to give that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then I want you to\Naccept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After which you get\Nto apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The King of the Pirates\Nwouldn't have any less
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,than the best on his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Big talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on, no matter\Nif I'm a criminal or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will spread the name\NZoro throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you standing\Nthere frozen for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to kill all\Nthree of them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You might wanna duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You knocked 'em all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna tell me what you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a guy who ate\Nthe Gum-Gum Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Gum-Gum Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A rubber person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he does have\Nthe Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we don't stand\Na chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just look at them!\NThey're insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't even take\Non Zoro by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Every marine that\Njust spouted weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,pull your gun out,\Nand shoot yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything\Nwith weak soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring those Marines\Ncrumbling to their knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY yells]\N--[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NRankless, low-life bums!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right\Nto defy my superiority!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Marine Captain\N"Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meetcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY grunts]\N--[MORGAN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. He's been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY grunts]\N--[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain's getting\Npummeled out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Call yourself a Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you destroyed my\Nfriend Coby's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY growls]\N--Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY grunts]\N--[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NAre ya stupid or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would pay\Nattention to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hostage here\Nyou might wanna look at!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your squatty\Nlittle friend's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious! One move and\NI'll shoot him! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anything that happens\Nto me stop you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that, you big idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Coby is ready to\Ndie by your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said don't move or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY] Behind you!\N--[LUFFY] Gum Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NTime's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For I am fearless Marine\NCaptain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, hurry up\Nand kill him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NPistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Just doing my job, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE A]\NCaptain Morgan's been beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE E]\NUnbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE C]\NThose guys are unreal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants to step forward\Nto fight us, then do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES gasping, murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE B]\NWe're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE F]\NFinally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE H]\NMorgan's reign is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE I]\NIt's really happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE G]\NGlorious day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're all happy\Nthat their captain was beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been afraid of him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time\Nbefore we showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, COBY gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NZoro! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NSorry, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to suck\Nit up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] I can't find\Nthis sucker anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NThat's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A maritime chart\Nof the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew they were hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NThis isn't the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What mark is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known on the seas...\Nas Buggy the Immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSPEOPLE chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhew! I am stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Having not eaten\Nfor three weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready to gnaw\Nthrough my boot straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[GROUP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell can you\Nhave a bigger appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,than a guy who hasn't\Neaten in weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] It just tastes too\Ngood, I guess. Right, Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for fixing it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you guys\Ndid save the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most amazing\Nman I've ever met!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be more amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I'm King of the Pirates,\Nand I have the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the best\Ncrew on the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How many others\Nhave you gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for your crew besides me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that you\Nwere in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of gathering together\Nthe crew for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're gonna be\NKing of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta assume you already\Nhave some waiting in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNope, just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. It's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you and I are what amounts\Nto an entire pirate crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a couple of strong guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But please tell me\Nyou have a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSure do. It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. But we'll have an\Nenormous one before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And how's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With a great big\Npirate flag on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Luffy was born\Nwithout that part of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that allows the rest of us to\Nplan out what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I let\Nmyself get suckered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,into having him as my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We'll have a ton more\Ncrewmembers in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NLuffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you and your\Ncrew planning on traveling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when you leave here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it's not obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed straight\Nfor the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Have you completely\Nlost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two crew members!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you're equipped\Nto handle the Grand Line, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never knew it was\Nsuch an awful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worse than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that this world\Nhas two oceans, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an enormous landmass\Nthat cuts across both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called the Red Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Legend tells of a town that sits\Ndead center on the Red Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is said\Nto cut through this town
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at a right angle and\Nstretch all the way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,around the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The story goes on to say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,had once obtained everything\Nthis world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he died, he said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that he left the great One Piece\Ntreasure at this location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, pirates have\Nset sail for the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Today the place is\Nnothing but a battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and some even call it\Nthe pirate graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard stories about it\Nfrom people passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The customers say that no one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who has ever entered\Nthe Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of\Nthat place alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is really too bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause that's where the\NOne Piece is said to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's exactly\Nwhere we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we have to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] What do you care, you're\Nnot going with us are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No... But I still worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so wrong to care\Nabout the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and I haven't known each\Nother for years or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd still consider\Nhim a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have to part ways but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] When I was a just little\Nkid, I never had any friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,much less anyone who would\Nbother fighting on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always tried my hardest\Nnever to fight for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] But the two of you\Nhave taught me a lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never learn on my own:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How to live for\Nwhat I believe in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've decided to make my\None childhood dream a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to\Njoin the Marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Then don't you think\Nyou should be a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,concerned with your situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you did spend two\Nyears on Alvida's pirate ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you were nothing\Nbut her cabin boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marines' information\Ngathering is top-notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find out about\Nyour time with Alvida,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll never join.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I... never thought of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NHey! You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY, RIKA gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard that you fellas\Nare actually pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this rumor true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, and I just added the\Nfirst member to my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty much the whole\Nthing just became official.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate everything you\Ndid to save our town from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that horrible tyrant who\Nterrorized us all for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now that we know that\Nyou're pirates, as Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot sit idly by and watch\Nyou go about your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you and your crew
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,will need to leave\Nthis town immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But out of respect for\Nwhat you've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we will not report\Nyou to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you find the\Nnerve to talk like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN B]\NBefore these pirates came along,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys were as scared\Nof Morgan as we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN A] Without them,\Nwe'd still be under his reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe them our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[TOWNSPEOPLE chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all\Nof the food, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second.\NYou're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT] Aren't you\Npart of the crew, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]\NUh, well, I... uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NHold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he with you or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What I can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is what he's been busy\Ndoing up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy! You wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was this\Nfantastically fat pirate lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think her name was Alvida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] If they find out\NI ran with a pirate crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never join the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She carried around this\Nhuge iron club and, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,she was the nastiest looking\Nwoman I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For two years, this wimpy kid\Nwas her own private cabin boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NPlease stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that was a dumb move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY, LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you pirates\Nripping up this town any more
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than you already\Nhave, you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NEnough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You made your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let him fall to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious you're not\Ncrewmates so stop badgering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the poor kid and take your leave\Nof our town this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NThat was on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy did that\Njust to help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] He worked me\Nup and got me so mad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd hit him and look\Nlike I wasn't on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] Even at the very\Nend of our journey together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wound up continuing\Nto rely on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do\Nanything for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed\Nfor me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NI am such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY] Sir!\N--[LIEUTENANT] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you have to let\Nme join the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean and scrub and do any\Nchores that you'd like me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything\Nto become a Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant. I can't say\NI fully trust this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be against the idea\Nif there weren't clear cases
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of certain Marines\Nactually being pirate spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, we should conduct\Na background check first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I am a\Nman who will become a Marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[reaction missing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT] I can't tell\Nyou how many of our comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,have been killed by\Npirates over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big step\Nyou're taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NPermission to join granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That was a thin act\Nyou put on back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if\Nthey see right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NCoby should be able
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle the rest on his own.\NI have faith in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] It is a fitting\Nway to leave this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,unable to turn back 'cause\Neveryone here hates us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very pirate-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COBY] Luffy!\N--[LUFFY] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done more for me\Nthan anyone ever has!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a Marine\Nthanking a pirate before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one for\Nthe history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWe'll meet again, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope to see you again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT] That's a good\Nfriend you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NMen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as our current salute\Nis in violation of Marine law,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we will all go without\Nfood for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we all understand this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES, COBY]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] I know that we'll\Nmeet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep inside, I feel it as much\Nas I've ever felt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,even if we are divided\Nas pirates and Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I still look\Nforward to that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, our pirate\Ncrew finally sets sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the feeling some\Ninteresting adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,are waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be King of the\NPirates. I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem more than obsessed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with this King of the\NPirates business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some kinda\Nstory behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any kind of reason at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo. No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised someone...\Na while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I swore that\NI would gather a crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,find the world's\Ngreatest treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and become King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this straw hat\Nknows the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to\Nset our heading...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYou're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know how\Nto navigate correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.09,0:24:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWell, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Ah! Would you\Nstop rocking the boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.68,0:24:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll knock my hat off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Is that straw hat\Nthat important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.31,0:24:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have to return it to him\Nafter I'm King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.39,0:24:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWho's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy's Past!\NEnter Red-Haired Shanks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

